U.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/USSMjFHk5TezYLmYbwGKHU.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDunelm has caught the eyes of shoppers with it\u0026#39;s vibrant colourful chair - it\u0026#39;s perfect if you\u0026#39;re looking for someting a little bolder.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s true the Oslo collapsing hanging chair isn’t as bright as the Santorini chair in soft Jade. The Santorini chair is available in blue and white shades, terracotta hues and a vibrant multi-coloured red, teal and yellow - making it perfect for your\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/boho-garden-decor-ideas-306284\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/boho-garden-decor-ideas-306284\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e boho garden ideas\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile the Oslo chair is available in more muted sage, natural and grey, I think it is perfect if you’re aiming for a more peaceful look. For many of us, gardens act as a place to relax, so it’s always worth opting for a calming hue when selecting your garden furniture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Oslo chair combines sleek design with comfort, including a plush inner cushion to sit on. Plus, it’s curved design means the chair holds you like a cocoon, providing ultimate comfort. It’s also collapsible, making it easy to store and well-designed for \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-ideas/small-garden-ideas-2-174377\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-ideas/small-garden-ideas-2-174377\"\u003e\u003cu\u003esmall garden ideas\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-320-80.png\" alt=\"Santorini egg chair on a patio\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/3me6m7T32daACrVKux9E4Z.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003eDunelm\u0026#39;s viral Santorini egg chair\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Dunelm)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Santorini chair is certainly a bolder choice, and I’d recommend it if you want to introduce more colour to your outdoor space. Combined with a rattan weave, the chair easily makes you feel like you’re on a sunny holiday. It’s easy to see why the chair is so popular -it truly is a thing of beauty, and with weather-resistant materials, it will bring colour on the greyest of days.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-iJgGRw3RHPBLAkEXYL4quX\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut I do think QVC’s Oslo chair is also an excellent choice - especially if you’re looking for an affordable yet quality item. Like the Santorini chair, it has a steel, powder-coated frame making it weather-resistant, but I think it’s collapsable element sets it apart from Dunelm in terms of practicality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-must-have-egg-chair-accessories\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMust-have egg chair accessories\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eHaving selected your perfect egg chair, you\u0026#39;ll want the perfect set-up to keep you lounging all summer long.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"3773dfd2-c7a2-4932-a99b-34a0af732688\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=1402\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-2870660934152823631\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marksandspencer.com%2Fset-of-2-geometric-outdoor-cushions%2Fp%2Fhbp60730159%3Fextid%3Dos_shopping_Furniture_UK_BAU%26srsltid%3DAfmBOoqnLXAQv9xum1VFn4k0PiCOypcxoWSuREWso1o2XhZdwTJ15lIP_4Q\" data-model-name=\"Set of 2 Geometric Outdoor Cushions\" data-url=\"https://www.marksandspencer.com/set-of-2-geometric-outdoor-cushions/p/hbp60730159?extid=os_shopping_Furniture_UK_BAU\u0026amp;srsltid=AfmBOoqnLXAQv9xum1VFn4k0PiCOypcxoWSuREWso1o2XhZdwTJ15lIP_4Q\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsore